text: Laraesima brunneoscutellaris is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Tippmann in 1960. It is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Laraesima brunneoscutellaris. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Compsosomatini Category:Beetles described in 1960
